Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:21.20,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向下一个舞台迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在贴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是西区的超市的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数字代表便当变成半价的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我个人推荐这两处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍克商场和常磐超市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道霍克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是昨晚你们在那战斗过的那家超市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说两边都很容易陷入激战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相应地 也是能让你们得到教育的好地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这两家超市都是我的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我就暂时先到别的地方去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们好运
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍克商场的半价神 油神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他贴完以前都不可以轻举妄动是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗有几条规则
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说 不能在半价神离开卖场前出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 贴完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在半价神离开卖场前出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 佐藤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:04:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.55,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}炸猪扒便当
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能猎取超过当晚自己吃的分量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 这就是“狼”的战斗方式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有着各种各样的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是全部都能归结于这一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵守礼仪 赌上尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下一家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 小狗们 今天过来这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 就是“狗”的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 光头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你又...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 没事 事实上就是这样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 老头要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老头？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这家超市的半价神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半价神也有老爷爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦克 是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要大地震了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等老头把半价贴纸贴完大概还要5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,络腮胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在我们的狩猎场可不能让那家伙乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是“大野猪”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则不起作用么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊 小狗们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 你们快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠你们是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶发女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没贴上半价贴纸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是全部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 店员先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快贴上贴纸啊 贴纸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是要贴 你就贴快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“猪”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知羞耻 却带着能横扫“狼”的獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是“野猪”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因为我们不够成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都想让老头幸福地结束一天的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼仪和尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是去买那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 昨天是这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...虽然是我碰过的 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然饭团还是要吃鲑鱼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这边也...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当虽然也很好吃 不过这个也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还是很想吃便当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然有点不甘心 不过没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是名副其实的“大野猪”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候该讲清楚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心里是怎么想白粉同学的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么又是这种像是要和情敌做个了断的台词？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白粉同学是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:10:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...我想确认一下 这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是字面意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么想的才会让她去争夺半价便当这种东西呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是我强制她的 她是自己决定...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她才不会积极地去干这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说 她实际上也这么做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以生气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是 你想说白粉同学认为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其跟我在一起 跟佐藤你在一起更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也没这样说...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以踢你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放弃 也不会认输的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白梅梅.. baibai
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再胡扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白粉她今天不过来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 刚才...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,u u u...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:02.07,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}梅在日语里面读做ume
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说小梅 小梅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的 那个...是我小学以来唯一的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一定是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我写的小说她也说很有趣 对我也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 当然不是指男欢女爱方面的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 为什么提起小梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才对我又是打巴掌又是踢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...就这样被带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 要等下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11连败 学姐你太强了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:11:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能成为“狼”就看你自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“狼”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:20.05,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}无标题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:20.05,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}今天的小梅很温柔 但总觉得有点可怕... ..·.（>_<）.·..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪边啊 看来又要惹白梅生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是“风暴”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“风暴”？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了迎接春天的比赛而开始进行练习的橄榄球社
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这群家伙要是来了的话 便当和素材就会全被他们抢光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所谓的天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去另一家店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强 别勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“风暴”再加上“大野猪”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧 放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那个人是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[魔导士]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[魔导士] 是“狼”吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这下真不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连魔导士都来了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...我在这里买井兵卫算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“大野猪”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“风暴”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[魔导士]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:14:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...你是说别买乌冬面 买荞麦面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想要成为“狼”吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要尝过一次血的味道 就再也变不回单纯的“狗”了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后也会忍受不了“猪”的屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵守礼仪 赌上尊严 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再让你往前一步的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在老头贴完贴纸以前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点 再撑一会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 老头大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔导士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中下怀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用对手的势头 再顺势避开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来已经结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 是“暴风”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当和素材 全都给我带走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？难道说这家伙是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[魔导士]！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 蠢猪们 今晚可没有饲料喂你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 不愧是[魔导士]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,络腮胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶发女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[狼]..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能让你们抢尽风头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“猪”才不配吃半价便当
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟这群狼纠缠 去抢便当！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月桂冠..就算拼了命也不能把月桂冠让给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月桂冠？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:42.81,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}月桂冠：半价便当中被半价神贴上特别贴纸的便当。视每家店不同贴上各自的贴纸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这群蠢猪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是目的还是礼仪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是尊严还是其他一切都忘掉了的一群蠢猪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱就该揍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪就该宰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了身为“狼”的矜持 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为“狼”的矜持？ 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书包忘在社团活动室了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白粉同学很消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是因为佐藤和学姐的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装傻吗？我要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天你就做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮件？是白粉发过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:16.19,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}学姐和佐藤同学都没有给我回复
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:16.19,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}是不是因为我写的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:16.19,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}很烦人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:16.19,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}很恶心？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:16.19,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}如果是的话 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是的话 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的 是因为白梅她会生气...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:27.00,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}写邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:27.00,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}To：白粉花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:27.00,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}RE:对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:27.51,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}有来电
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:27.51,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}未知号码
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了 你是恶意骚扰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让我把你的手机变成废铁吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这样做了对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 有了 有了 书包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚接到了一个相当绕圈子的像是杀人预告的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白粉她现在是什么情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白梅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐 难道说你在等我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？算是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说昨天也是在这里...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次胜利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻起来不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味增煮青花鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这是什么东西才拿的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个便当上贴的是月桂冠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月桂冠？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是半价神在剩下的便当里面挑出最有自信的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再在上面贴上的特别的贴纸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在存在着月桂冠的领域里的人都会以这个为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当天得到这个的人会成为该领域里面绝对的胜利者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次胜利就拿到月桂冠 说不定你能成大器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧 毕竟对手是“暴风”嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:20:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 被称为[魔导士]的“狼”有过来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[魔导士]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是这学校的三年级生 叫金城优
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就先记住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金城优？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 有这么多月桂冠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一张都装满了回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再慢慢说给你听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 自己亲手贴上去吧 佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要写上日期和名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 细细品尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先说“我开动了”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对把它做出来的人 把它变成半价的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及成为了食材的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}还有对那些同样很想得到手却被你夺走了的人们的敬意和感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我开动了
